            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Producing 10 social posts in a batched session typically takes about 2 hours. Scattered creation throughout the week runs 4+ hours for the same output. Batching cuts creation time by 50% on average due to reduced context-switching.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

